    • addDefaultObjects

      void addDefaultObjects(PipelineData pipelineData)
      Adds some convenience objects to the request. For example an instance of JspLink which can be used to generate links to other templates.
      Parameter:
      pipelineData - the Turbine PipelineData object

    • handleRequest

      void handleRequest(PipelineData pipelineData, String templateName, boolean isForward) throws TurbineException
      executes the JSP given by templateName.
      Parameter:
      pipelineData - A PipelineData Object
      templateName - The template to execute
      isForward - whether to perform a forward or include.
      Löst aus:
      TurbineException - If a problem occurred while executing the JSP
